---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const title = "Discovering Saint-Tropez and the Gulf | Guide";
const description = "English guide to reach Saint-Tropez and the Gulf area, enjoy the beaches and villages, and avoid traffic and parking stress.";
const canonical = "/en/guide-saint-tropez-and-gulf.html";
---

<BaseLayout 
  title={title}
  description={description}
  currentPage="guide-saint-tropez-and-gulf"
  canonical={canonical}
>

    <nav class="breadcrumbs container" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
      <a href="/en/">Home</a> › <a href="/en/guides">VTC Guides</a> › <span>Saint-Tropez and the Gulf</span>
    </nav>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-header">
          <div class="section-eyebrow">Saint-Tropez guide</div>
          <h1 class="section-title">Discovering Saint-Tropez and the Gulf</h1>
          <p>Reaching Saint-Tropez can take time in high season. With a bit of planning, you can still enjoy the area without turning your stay into a busy commute.</p>
        </div>

        <section class="section" style="padding-top:1.5rem">
          <h2>Reaching the area</h2>
          <p>Traffic can be heavy on certain days and at certain hours. If possible, try to:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>avoid peak weekend times for your main transfers;</li>
            <li>group several activities on the same day instead of going back and forth;</li>
            <li>clarify your pick-up and drop-off locations with your driver.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="section" style="padding-top:1.5rem">
          <h2>Enjoying beaches and villages</h2>
          <p>The Gulf of Saint-Tropez offers a mix of beaches, small villages and viewpoints. A private driver can help you move between them without worrying about parking or narrow roads.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="section" style="padding-top:1.5rem">
          <h2>Evenings and late returns</h2>
          <p>If you plan to go out for dinner or to a club, it is usually easier to book your return in advance. This way you know someone will be waiting for you at the agreed time and place.</p>
          <p>To explain your plans, you can simply use the <a href="/reservation">booking form</a> and mention the main locations and approximate times.</p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </section>
  
</BaseLayout>
